            "content": "<p>Lucira’s designs often blend the purity of fine craftsmanship with modern sensibilities - making them suitable for every style preference. You can also visit Lucira’s experience stores in <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur</span></a>, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sky-city-borivali-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Mumbai</span></a>, or <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/pune-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">JM Road, Pune</span></a>, or explore their online store to see how these variations come to life through personalized design consultations.</p>",
