            "content": "<p>For an effortlessly coordinated ensemble, consider pairing hoops with a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <strong>l</strong>ab grown diamond necklace </a>a modern, sustainable twist on classic luxury.</p>",
